metadata.name: Elementum
metadata.description:
A new multidisciplinary work where each element has its unique meaning.  
First level: The waves, they symbolize the environment for an artist to try to balance his work with marketing every time he has to.  
Second level: The good and the bad, these opposite sides, we never recognize at first but with time we get saturated with.  
And finally the last level, which is the artist, he who feels the competition and always competes with other artists rather than himself, in hopes of elevating his craft.  
Enjoy!!!
